   leakage.

MATTERS OF DEGREE ARE NOT FAILURES. Register, rhythm, metaphor quality, and
"too literary / too spare" judgments are taste; a writer cannot converge on
taste under a two-round limit. If the prose is honest, complete, and inside the
voice's hard rules, pass it — even prose you would have written differently.

